### SGR File Agent API Tests
### ============================================
### This file contains HTTP requests for testing the SGR File Agent
### Use REST Client extension in VS Code to execute these requests
###
### Prerequisites:
### 1. Install REST Client extension in VS Code
### 2. Start server: sgr --config-file examples/sgr_file_agent/config.yaml
### 3. Click "Send Request" above any request to execute it
###
### Response Headers:
### - X-Agent-ID: Agent identifier (use for state/clarification requests)
### - X-Agent-Model: Model name used
###
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8010
@agentModel = sgr_file_agent

### Variables (update these as needed)
### Replace {{agentId}} with actual agent ID from X-Agent-ID response header
@agentId = sgr_file_agent_12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012

###############################################################################
# Health Check & Info
###############################################################################

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get Available Models (Agents)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/models

### Get Agents List
GET {{baseUrl}}/agents

###############################################################################
# File Agent - Basic Operations
###############################################################################

POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "{{agentModel}}",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Find all Python files in the current directory"
    }
  ],
  "stream": true,
  "temperature": 0.4
}
